Three API Tasks using Promises:

1. Cat Images Viewer (Cat API)
   Description:
   Fetches and displays 10 random cat images.
   Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, BOOTSTARP, JAVASCRPIT.
   API Information:
   API: The Cat API
   URL: https://api.thecatapi.com/v1/images/search?limit=20
   Data: Random cat images.

2. Country Data Viewer (REST Countries API)
   Description:
   Fetches and displays all countries information like flags, country names, population and region.
   Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, BOOTSTARP, JAVASCRPIT.
   API Information:
   API: REST Countries API
   URL: https://restcountries.com/v3.1/all
   Data: Country information which includes flags, names, populations, and regions.

3. Random Jokes Viewer (Official Joke API)
   Description:
   Fetches and displays 10 random jokes.
   Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, BOOTSTARP, JAVASCRPIT.
   API Information:
   API: Official Joke API
   URL: https://official-joke-api.appspot.com/random_ten
   Data: Random jokes.
